ğŸ¯ Functional Requirements
ğŸ”¹ Student Management
    Add student

    View all students

    Delete student (by ID)

Business rules:

    Student name cannot be empty

    Duplicate student names not allowed

ğŸ”¹ Course Management
    Add course

    View all courses

    Delete course (by ID)

Business rules:

    Course name must be unique

    Course name cannot be empty

ğŸ”¹ Enrollment Management (Most Important Part)
    Enroll a student in a course

    View all enrollments

    Remove enrollment

Business rules (Service Layer rules):

    Student must exist

    Course must exist

    A student cannot be enrolled in the same course twice

    If a student is deleted â†’ their enrollments must be deleted

    If a course is deleted â†’ related enrollments must be deleted

